            <p>Current User Agreement is an integral part of NewAgeZ Gaming Portal. The User is obligated to check the Agreement at least once a week. Disagreement, even with one of the current rules, does not allow you to use this Gaming Portal. It is necessary to follow the rules, for everyone User of Gaming Portal, regardless of whether User  is registered or not.</p>
